<span id="fn_747"></span>[256:4](sbe4544.htm#fr_753.md) Mahâvîra.

<span id="fn_748"></span>[256:5](sbe4544.htm#fr_754.md) Âhitam, literally,
has been declared. The commentators explain the word as â-hitam,
thoroughly good, or âtmani vyavasthitam, placed in the soul.

<span id="fn_749"></span>[257:1](sbe4544.htm#fr_755.md) Samprasâraka?

<span id="fn_750"></span>[257:2](sbe4544.htm#fr_756.md) *Kh*anna = mâyâ.

<span id="fn_751"></span>[257:3](sbe4544.htm#fr_757.md) Pasa*m*sa =
